  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK688">
<l>tūymai tuṇaimai tuṇivuṭaimai yimmūṉṟiṉ </l>
<l>vāymai vaḻiyuraippāṉ paṇpu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The qualifications of him who faithfully delivers his (sovereign's) message are purity, the support (of foreign ministers), and boldness, with truthfulness in addition to the (aforesaid) three.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
